| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-3369 — Recovery Inhibition (aurora)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 0af63774-eccd-5d68-a4d1-1ef76e440d83"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
